videos.description: Justin Herbert lets it fly to Johnny Johnson III for a 47-yard gain, setting up CJ Verdell's 1-yard touchdown on 4th down.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Herbert's heave sets up Verdell TD) 2019/8/31

videos.headline: Herbert's heave sets up Verdell TD

videos.description: Bryan Addison can't handle Justin Herbert's pinpoint pass for a potential touchdown, and Camden Lewis fails to hit the 20-yard field goal.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Addison drops Herbert's wide-open TD, Lewis shanks FG) 2019/8/31

videos.headline: Addison drops Herbert's wide-open TD, Lewis shanks FG

videos.description: Justin Herbert's 50-50 ball to the end zone is hauled in by Spencer Webb, who steps over an Auburn defender after the 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Webb steps over defender after snagging TD from Herbert

videos.description: Bo Nix forces a pass on the run and is intercepted by Thomas Graham Jr., ending Auburn's red zone threat.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn's Nix gets picked off in red zone) 2019/8/31

videos.headline: Auburn's Nix gets picked off in red zone

videos.description: Justin Herbert's fake to CJ Verdell is fumbled and Big Kat Bryant sucks up the loose ball and chugs it 83 yards before being tackled.
videos.headline: Herbert's fumble nearly brought back for long TD

videos.description: Bo Nix's deep ball is underthrown and intercepted by Jevon Holland for Nix's second pick of the game.
videos.headline: Nix throws 2nd pick of half

videos.description: Darrian Felix takes the handoff on the jet sweep and bursts to the end zone for a six-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Felix cuts to edge for Oregon TD) 2019/8/31

videos.headline: Felix cuts to edge for Oregon TD

videos.description: Bo Nix takes advantage of Oregon's defensive blunder and slings an 11-yard touchdown to Eli Stove.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nix throws 1st career TD to Stove) 2019/8/31

videos.headline: Nix throws 1st career TD to Stove

videos.description: Joey Gatewood's number is called on 1st-and-goal as he leaps and breaks the plane for an Auburn touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gatewood flies into end zone for goal-line TD) 2019/8/31

videos.headline: Gatewood flies into end zone for goal-line TD

videos.description: Bo Nix flings a 26-yard touchdown to Seth Williams to put Auburn up 27-21 with nine seconds remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nix rips game-winning TD to Williams in final seconds) 2019/8/31

videos.headline: Nix rips game-winning TD to Williams in final seconds

videos.description: In his first collegiate game, Auburn's Bo Nix tosses the game-winning touchdown with less than 10 seconds remaining to defeat Justin Herbert and the Ducks.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Nix's heroics lead to Auburn's comeback win over Oregon) 2019/8/31 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Nix's heroics lead to Auburn's comeback win over Oregon

videos.description: Bo Nix expresses how special his game-winning touchdown was in his first career start which propelled Auburn past Oregon.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Nix: Game-winning TD was 'surreal moment') 2019/8/31

videos.headline: Nix: Game-winning TD was 'surreal moment'
